        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownRiftenFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionRiften\")",
        "content": "Redbelly Mine is the iron mine beneath Shor's Stone village. Filnjar oversees the work; his daughter Sylgja is one of the miners. Frostbite spiders sometimes invade the lower shaft and shut the operation down until someone clears them out.",
        "display_name": "Redbelly Mine - Iron (Shor's Stone)",
        "emotion": "",
